    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ride as world champion and MTB legend Sam Pilgrim, using an advanced trick system to bust out insane combos across 40+ hand-crafted levels designed to capture the “flow” of mountain biking.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With zero BS getting between you and the action, <strong>Shred! 2</strong> can be a quick “one more go” session or a deep dive into longer shredding runs. It’s an addictive, authentic MTB experience where every inch of trail pushes you to the limit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Created out of pure passion for the sport by a solo developer, <strong>Shred! 2 delivers one of the most genuine MTB gameplay experiences out there.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ride &amp; Customise bikes...lots of Bikes!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ride official Canyon bikes, including the Stitched 360, Stitched 720, Spectral, Torque, and Sender! Plus unlock a whole range of custom creations—from clean modern builds to full-on ridiculous contraptions. Ever wanted to launch a mini bike off a cliff? Or tailwhip a tandem? Now you can. Sam the man would be proud.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/853200/extras/58cc40d2b77ab1cefd8f73be042196da.avif?t=1764800116\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/853200/extras_big/58cc40d2b77ab1cefd8f73be042196da.webp?t=1764800116 width=1560 height=1508 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Over 40 levels &amp; 200 unique challenges</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on 40 hand-crafted levels spanning diverse MTB disciplines, including Downhill, Slopestyle, and Street riding <strong> inspired by MTB culture, riding destinations, events and video segments!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ride across the UK, USA, the High Alps, and “<strong>The Zone</strong>” — a 